_sText:
Im hoping everyone enjoys this update release of my first-ever CSS map.

CHANGELOG

---v2_fix2---
* Moved the new vent system up higher so it is only accessible from lower levels
* The second and third level of tubes were removed.
* General map optimizations were included.

---v2_fix1---
* Moved elevator and torture room to better place
* Added new vent system to move around the map
* Tubes added to the warehouse along with player clips to prevent players doing stuff that would make it nearly impossible for zombies to get them
* Improved some glitchy lighting issues
* Removed secret button to access secure room near T spawn, instead the door can be opened by use until I can add a keypad in later version.
* Combine op center optimised for performance, less crap on that level.

Basically evened the map out for both teams a bit :).
